In 100 days, athletes from all over the world will be competing in different events in alpine skiing, freestyle skiing and snowboarding at the 2022 Winter Olympic Games in China. They will attend 11 events in alpine skiing to conquer different trails, going through a number of twists at high speed. They will have 13 freestyle skiing golds to compete for while showing the world how many tricks they can complete while leaping into the air. If skiing is not exciting enough, many will attend 11 of the above events on snowboards, which requires a completely different set of skills. Host: Li Xiang Guest: Sim Sim Wissgott Cover designer: Feng Yuan Chief editor: Chen Ran Supervisor: Zhang Shilei